data.description: Here's your chance to break the cycle of renting and start owning at a location that cannot be beat- The Marquis at Vienna Metro !  No need to drive to the metro station anymore, it's right across the street from your new place to call home.  This spacious two bedroom & two bath Oxford Model condo features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, large island, clever office alcove w/custom shelving,  owners walk-in closet specially by California Closets & washer/dryer in unit.  Private covered garage parking  with 2 designated spaces & 2 visitor parking passes convey with this home. If you're looking for a community that is rich in the amenities it offers its' residents, look no further-- you'll be pleasantly surprised by the indoor basketball court,  gym,  pool/game room, office/media room, outdoor pool, clubhouse, bbq area in gated courtyard and a business center. Condo fee covers trash + water & a Home Warranty Conveys.
